Content-Type: application/json

{
  "class_id": "{{class_id}}",
  "hour": "M",
  "week_day": "MON"
}

###
# @name get_all_class_schedules
GET http://localhost:8000/classes/{{class_id}}/schedules HTTP/1.1

###
