###
# @name delete_class_schedule
DELETE http://localhost:8000/classes/{{class_id}}/schedules/{{schedule_id}} HTTP/1.1

###
# @name change_class_schedule
PUT http://localhost:8000/classes/{{class_id}}/schedules/{{schedule_id}} HTTP/1.1
